title: CAN'T GET TO THE LOGIN PAGE!?
body:
Hi guys after the 5.17 patch, I just can't seem to get to the Login page. 

Nothing happens when I click on the "Launch" button.

Sometimes, I will get the "REVIEW THIS EULA" page  & the "REVIEW THIS DISCLAIMER" page but when I click "Accept", nothing happens and I'm still staring at the Launch page. 

I've been through the Wrenchman's Toolbox.

I have tried all the possible solutions suggested  in this link: http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report/J6MZxxyL-when-i-click-launch-nothing-happens 

and this link: http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report/YTYXWqNl-league-wont-open-after-clicking-launch-may-have-found-a-partial-solutionclue

I've re-installed LoL, added exceptions to my antivirus/firewall, run multiple virus, spyware, malware scans.  I have literally tried everything and nothing bloody works. 

Help?

replies.body: did this get resolved i'm experiencing the same problem..

Yikes, sounds like an odd case!

Gather up the logs from [this page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752674-Network-System-and-League-of-Legends-Logs) (especially your Process List), and then send it our way through a [Player Support request](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new). I have some friends on the tech team there who can work with you to find a solution!
